title: Overturned lorry causes delays in Cardiff
text:
Emergency services are attending an incident involving an overturned lorry in Cardiff near the Butetown Tunnels.
The fire services says "expect delays".
An overturned lorry near the Butetown Tunnel is causing delays. Credit: Google Street View SW Fire & Rescue @SWFireandRescue Follow #SWControl attending a road traffic collision, lorry overturned at Cardiff Retail Park, bottom of Link Road, expect delays. hp
